sentences.english: Intergrowth relationship is the unity of individual and community.
sentences.chinese: 共生關係是共同體與個體的統一。

sentences.english: Ultra-structure of symbiosis mycorrhizal between cymbidium goeringii and rhizoctonia sp.
sentences.chinese: 春蘭與絲核菌共生菌根及結構研究。

sentences.english: It is a symbiotic relationship that has worked well for millions of years.
sentences.chinese: 這個互利共生的關係已經持續了千百萬年。

sentences.english: It is a symbiotic relationship that is unlikely to change anytime soon.
sentences.chinese: 這種共生關係在短期內不大可能發生變化。

sentences.english: There may be symbiotic advantages to chronic infections with these viruses.
sentences.chinese: 慢性感染這些病毒可能有共生的好處。

sentences.english: This is the first documented case of a plant living in partnership, or symbiosis, with a vertebrate.
sentences.chinese: 這是首個被記錄在案的植物與脊椎動物共生的例子。

sentences.english: And in the end, both mixotrophs and phototrophs tended to fare better when living together.
sentences.chinese: 而這兩類生物體也往往在共生時生長的更好。

sentences.english: Viruses themselves are sometimes taken in symbiotically.
sentences.chinese: 病毒自身有時候也被納入共生。

sentences.english: A newly refashioned symbiotic relationship between the two adversaries was born.
sentences.chinese: 一個新的，在兩個敵人間的共生關係誕生。

sentences.english: The nanon size texture is one of intergrowth crystals of cubic and hexagonal diamonds.
sentences.chinese: 這種織構通常是立方和六方金剛石的共生晶體。

sentences.english: So Wegner had to live with the pencil in her head.
sentences.chinese: 因此，維格納只好讓鉛筆留在腦內與她共生。

sentences.english: Phylogenetic analysis suggested this Gymnodinium-like species is a Symbiodinium species.
sentences.chinese: 進化分析初步鑑定該藻爲一種共生甲藻。

sentences.english: This is a paragenesis, we can get various minerals at one time.
sentences.chinese: 這是座共生礦，我們可以一次獲取多種礦石。

sentences.english: Politicians use the "right" making money, black and white confluence, Living and sharing interests.
sentences.chinese: 政治人物藉“權”撈錢，黑白合流，利益共生互享。

sentences.english: Intergrowth of mankind and geographical conditions.
sentences.chinese: 人類與地理環境的共生。

sentences.english: METHODS Blood-perfused parabiotic isolated rabbit heart langendorff model were used.
sentences.chinese: 方法採用間生態離體兔心共生支持系統模型。
